<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><TimeML><TIMEX3 tid="t0" functionInDocument="CREATION_TIME"/>Severiano Ballesteros has <EVENT eid="e1" class="I_ACTION" tense="PRESENT" aspect="PERFECTIVE" polarity="POS" modality="none">called</EVENT> for a <EVENT eid="e2" class="OCCURRENCE" tense="NONE" aspect="NONE" polarity="POS" modality="none">decision</EVENT> on  the venue for the <TIMEX3 tid="t1" type="DATE">1997</TIMEX3> Ryder Cup to be <EVENT eid="e3" class="I_ACTION" tense="INFINITIVE" aspect="NONE" polarity="POS" modality="none">postponed</EVENT> after claims which could  <EVENT eid="e4" class="OCCURRENCE" tense="NONE" aspect="NONE" polarity="POS" modality="could">ammount</EVENT> to allegations of bribery.&#13;
